So, I wonder if his taillights got moisture in them on his drive home and if his headlights have the residue issue inside the lens. The Dash still sucks... totally sucks...looks cheap like a $20K car with a tablet smacked into it... I would rather have a 'Real' dash and a smaller screen like a 10" built into the radio. I wish they would do a dash like the Porshe Taycan, that car has a beautiful interior but at that price, it is expected, so let's go back to the $40k models...
if we look in the $40K range I would much rather have an interior like the
2020 Lexus UX
2020 Infiniti QX50
2020 Acura RDX
and so ... from the front seat drivers view the interior of the Tesla looks just so damn cheap with an oversized tablet sticking out... you can't deny how cheap it looks and it looks really bad when you compare it to other cars in the price range.
